    {
      "id": "/page/0/Text/15",
      "block_type": "Text",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Text\">The fair value can be derived using the volatility formula discussed in [4]. In this reference, the authors show the remarkable formula that the expected value of any smooth payoff function <i>f (ST</i> <i>)</i> in terms of the terminal stock price <i>ST</i> can be written in terms of stock and option prices.</p>",
