    {
      "id": "/page/1/Text/21",
      "block_type": "Text",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Text\">The first piece is just the time-weighted value of realized variance against the strike. The second piece is the time-weighted difference of fair value variance strikes. The same formula can be used to decompose the daily price change into three risk components: gamma, vega, and theta:</p>",
