      "id": "/page/1/Equation/22",
      "block_type": "Equation",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Equation\"><math display=\"block\">\\Delta M(t) = M(t + \\Delta t) - M(t)</math>\n<math display=\"block\">= N \\left( \\underbrace{\\frac{1}{\\tau} V(t, t + \\Delta t) \\Delta t}_{\\text{Gamma}} + \\underbrace{(1 - \\lambda_{t + \\Delta t}) \\cdot \\Delta K}_{\\text{Vega}} - \\underbrace{\\frac{1}{\\tau} K_t \\Delta t}_{\\text{Theta}} \\right) \\qquad (15)</math></p>",
